| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-5943 — Recovery Inhibition (bianlian)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 2f976e6e-381d-5d02-b857-3dd4323cedf9"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
